{This was a simultaneous exhibition.} 1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4 Nf6 $5 4. Ng5 (4. d3 $14) (4. O-O Nxe4 5. Nc3 Nxc3 6. dxc3 Qe7 $1 $17) (4. d4 {Lange,M}) 4... d5 5. exd5 Na5 (5... Nd4 $5 {Fritz,A}) (5... b5 $5 {Ulvestad,O}) (5... Nxd5 6. d4 $1 $40 (6. Nxf7 $5)) 6. Bb5+ c6 7. dxc6 bxc6 8. Be2 h6 9. Nh3 $5 {Steinitz,W} Bc5 (9... Bd6 {Steinitz,W} 10. d4 {Chigorin,M} e4 {Fischer,R}) (9... Bf5 10. O-O Qd7 11. Re1 Bxh3 12. gxh3 Qxh3 13. Bf1 Qg4+ $2 14. Qxg4 Nxg4 15. h3 $18 {Steinitz,W}) (9... g5 10. d3 g4 {This is premature.} ({We would choose} 10... Bg7 {because he cannot castle} 11. O-O ({So he would go} 11. Ng1 {by himself.} O-O 12. Nc3 ({There is no} 12. h4 {because of} g4) 12... Rb8 {Adding some energy. I am always dreaming about Rb4 rook lifts.} 13. Nf3 Nd5 14. O-O Re8 {With good compensation.}) 11... g4) 11. Ng1 Bc5 12. Nc3 Qb6 13. Na4 $1) 10. O-O (10. d3 $1 {} O-O 11. Nc3 Re8 12. O-O Bxh3 13. gxh3 Qd7 14. Bg4 Nxg4 15. hxg4 {Fischer,R-Radoicic,M Poughkeepsie 1963}) 10... O-O (10... g5 11. Kh1 g4 12. Ng1 Ne4 13. Bxg4 $1 (13. b4 Nxf2+ (13... Bxf2 14. d3 Qh4 15. dxe4 Bg3 16. Nh3 (16. h3 gxh3 17. gxh3 Rg8) 16... Bxh2 $1 17. Kxh2 g3+ 18. Kg1 Bxh3) 14. Rxf2 Bxf2 15. bxa5 Qh4 $1 16. Qf1 Bg3 17. h3 Rg8 $19 {}) (13. Qe1 Qd4 14. Bd1 Nxf2+ 15. Rxf2 Qxf2 16. Qxe5+ $2 Be6) 13... Nxf2+ 14. Rxf2 Bxf2 $14 {Gottschall,H}) 11. d3 Bxh3 {} (11... Nd5 12. c4 Ne7 13. Kh1 Bxh3 14. gxh3 Nf5 15. f4 exf4 16. Bxf4 Ne3 17. Bxe3 Bxe3 18. Nc3 $18 {Steinitz,W-Chigorin,M (6) Habana WCH 1892}) (11... Nh7 {Gottschall,H}) 12. gxh3 {Fischer allowed this and won very fast.} Qd7 13. Bf3 (13. Bg4 Nxg4 14. hxg4 f5 $40) (13. Kg2) 13... Qxh3 14. Nd2 (14. Bg2 Qh4 $1 15. Qe1 Rfe8 $1 16. Qxa5 Ng4 17. h3 Bxf2+ 18. Rxf2 (18. Kh1 Qg3) 18... Qxf2+ 19. Kh1 e4 $1 20. hxg4 (20. dxe4 Rxe4) 20... exd3 $19) 14... Rad8 (14... e4 $2 15. Nxe4 Nxe4 16. Bxe4 Bd6 17. f4) 15. Bg2 {I would not trust Fischer's position though. I think Black is doing very well.} Qf5 (15... Qh4 $2 16. Nf3 Qh5 17. Qe1) 16. Qe1 (16. Qf3) 16... Rfe8 {I would prefer the Black pieces because we have a lot of activity.} 17. Ne4 Bb6 18. Nxf6+ (18. b4 Nb7 19. b5) 18... Qxf6 19. Kh1 c5 {I don't like this move.} (19... g5 {;  Na5-...-h4 }) 20. Qc3 $1 (20. Qe2 {Gegen c4 gerichtet. c3 verhindert Nc6-d4, Be3, Rg1, Be4 g-Linie} c4 21. dxc4 e4 $1 22. Rb1 (22. Bxe4 $4 Qe5 23. f3 f5 $19) 22... Bc7 $36 {Agur}) (20. Bd2 Nc6 21. Qe4 Nd4 22. c3 Nf5 23. Qc4 Nd6 (23... Nh4 24. Be4 g5 $5 $14) 24. Qg4 c4 $1 (24... e4 25. dxe4 Nxe4 26. Be3) 25. dxc4 e4 26. Be3 Nxc4 27. Bxb6 (27. Rab1 Bxe3 28. fxe3 Qg5 $1 $36) 27... axb6 $36) 20... Nc6 (20... g5 $2 21. f4 $1) 21. f4 Nd4 22. Qc4 $1 (22. fxe5 Qxe5 23. Bf4 Qe2) 22... Qg6 { Qh5; Nf5} (22... Qe6 23. Qa4 Qd7 $2 24. Qxd7 Rxd7 25. c3 Nc2 26. Bc6 $1) 23. c3 (23. Be4 Qh5 24. f5 Qe2 25. Rg1 Nf3 $1) 23... Nf5 (23... Ne2 24. f5 Qf6 (24... Qh5 $2 25. Bf3 $1) 25. Be3 Nf4 26. Be4) 24. fxe5 (24. Be4 Qh5 $13) 24... Rxe5 25. Bf4 (25. Qf4 Bc7 $1 26. Be4 Qh5 $1) 25... Re2 (25... Ne3 26. Bxe3 Rxe3 $10) 26. Be4 Rxb2 $2 (26... Re8 $1 {;  R8xe4} 27. Rg1 (27. Bf3 {} Rxb2 28. Rae1 $10 {}) 27... Qh5 28. Raf1 Ne3 $1 29. Qb5 Rxe4 30. dxe4 Nxf1 31. Qe8+ (31. Rxf1 Qg4 $19) 31... Kh7 32. Rxg7+ Kxg7 33. Be5+ Qxe5 34. Qxe5+ f6 35. Qe7+ Kg6 36. Qe8+ Kg5 $19) 27. Be5 $1 $18 Re8 28. Rxf5 Rxe5 29. Rxe5 1-0

