1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4 Nf6 4. d3 h6 5. O-O d6 6. c3 g6 7. Re1 Bg7 8. a4 O-O 9. a5 a6 10. b4 Kh8 (10... Kh7 $144 11. Nbd2 Nh5 12. Nf1 f5 13. exf5 Bxf5 $36) 11. Qb3 $6 Qe7 $6 {It wasn't necessary to protect the pawn:} (11... Nh5 $1 $15 12. Bxf7 $2 Qf6 13. Bc4 g5 $17) (11... Nh7 $1 $15) 12. Nbd2 Nh7 13. Nf1 (13. Bd5 f5 14. Bxc6 bxc6 $40) 13... f5 14. Ne3 f4 $1 15. Nd5 Qd8 $17 {The knight looks good on d5 but doesn't do much to help White: There is a mating attack underway and he hardly has any pieces participating in the defence.} 16. Bb2 g5 17. Nd2 g4 18. Nf1 h5 (18... Ng5 $1 {looks even better:} 19. d4 f3 $1 20. Ng3 (20. g3 Nh3+ $19) 20... fxg2 21. Kxg2 Nf3 22. Rh1 Qh4 $19) 19. b5 axb5 20. Qxb5 h4 21. a6 Rb8 $1 22. Nb4 Nxb4 23. Qxb4 g3 24. fxg3 hxg3 25. Bd5 f3 $1 26. gxf3 Ng5 $1 27. Nxg3 Nxf3+ 28. Kh1 Nxe1 29. Rxe1 Bh6 $2 30. Bxb7 Bf4 31. a7 Bxb7 32. axb8=Q Qxb8 33. Bc1 c5 34. Qc4 Bxg3 35. hxg3 Qc8 36. Kg2 Qg4 37. Rh1+ Kg7 38. Bh6+ 1-0

